"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-david-wise-ski-halfpipe-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"For years, people have asked David Wise how long he thinks he can make a career out of halfpipe skiing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wise_(composer)\", \"score\": 0.4456146524189075, \"rank\": 0.6398221343875826, \"text\": \"David Wise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wise_(composer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wise_(composer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always said, I do not know how long I can do this for,\\\" Wise said.\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will let you know when I get there.\\\"\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's almost there.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise, an Olympic gold medalist in 2014 and 2018 and silver medalist in 2022, is in his last Olympic cycle.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He plans to retire after either the 2026 Milan Cortina Games (he must still qualify for the deep U.S. team) or, should he tack it on, a less-intense farewell 2026-27 season.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Part of me was wondering going into Beijing (in 2022) if it was going to be my last Olympics,\\\" said Wise, a 34-year-old from Reno, Nevada, who has a 13-year-old daughter and 10-year-old son.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.99999891076882, \"rank\": 1.0892323048676702e-06, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawlor_Events_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7383599329809708e-13, \"text\": \"Reno, Nevada\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawlor_Events_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawlor_Events_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawlor_Events_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7383599329809708e-13, \"text\": \"Reno, Nevada\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawlor_Events_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawlor_Events_Center\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything comes at a cost.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While I think I have the best job in the world, my kids and wife pay the price because I am gone a lot.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we definitely did some soul-searching and dug deep.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was honest, and I said I do not feel like my fuel tank is empty.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I still love this job.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to do something to keep the lights on in the house.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to try to do this one more time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Dec. 7, Wise made his first ski halfpipe podium in nearly two years.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This weekend, he competes at the Toyota U.S. Grand Prix at Copper Mountain.An NBC Sports and Peacock broadcast schedule is here.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota_Racing_(Formula_One_team)\", \"score\": 0.9992194706773534, \"rank\": 0.0005560804145001503, \"text\": \"Toyota\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota_Racing_(Formula_One_team)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota_Racing_(Formula_One_team)\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999946708158, \"rank\": 5.271066632039799e-09, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999853525879, \"rank\": 1.4621774883728698e-08, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise is one of, if not the last active freeskier who knows what it's like to compete on the sport's highest level before that level was the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He made his Winter X Games debut in 2011, six months before the IOC announced that ski halfpipe and ski slopestyle were added to the Olympic program for the 2014 Sochi Games.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.864154207022385e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise is the only freeskier to win gold at two Olympics and the only American man to win two golds and a silver across all skiing events.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998509509372359, \"rank\": 0.0001125981284738463, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2022 Beijing Games, he was edged out for gold by Nico Porteous of New Zealand.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.403186446247457, \"rank\": 0.7812545553055321, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In January 2023, he won the X Games for his first major title in five years.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two months later, he tore his right ACL in what was already planned to be the last run of his 2022-23 season at the World Championships.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\", \"score\": 0.9964924277141018, \"rank\": 0.003519918655036285, \"text\": \"ACL\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q39888\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kind of was staring the sunset of my career in the face anyway, and then I had sustained another super long-term recovery injury,\\\" said Wise, who broke the femur in the same leg in 2019.\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was kind of asking myself and asking God and asking my family, is this the indication?\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never wanted to be in denial when it came time to retire.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not ever want to be in denial about it.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So some of that was just me being honest with myself.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do I want to fight?\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do I want to work my ass off and come back from this injury and try to stay relevant and try to make another Olympic team?\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or do I want to take this as an excuse to retire and still heal my knee and be a functioning athletic human, but not a high-level athlete ever again?\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I just do not.\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't born with quit in me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise returned for the 2023-24 season, which he called the least successful of his career results-wise.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was 100% physically recovered but never felt confident.\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not finish on the podium across six events.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This fall, Wise was joined by daughter Nayeli for his preseason training in Europe for the first time.\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she had pigtails, she used to think every skier on TV was her dad.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's almost more of a travel buddy,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's not as dependent on me for her everyday, momentary needs.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I just feel really fortunate to still be able to do what I do for a living and kind of include the family as much as I can.\\\"\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then on Dec. 7, Wise placed third in his season debut in China as part of a historic podium.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3543, \"end\": 3548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7021472959811361, \"rank\": 0.2248132321972907, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only was ita U.S. sweep, but it was also made up of three men in their 30s for the first time in World Cup ski halfpipe history.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise broke his own record as the oldest man to make a podium in the discipline.\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"China, for me, was the first time I really felt like myself on skis again,\\\" since the March 2023 ACL tear, he said.\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3795, \"end\": 3800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7021472959811361, \"rank\": 0.2248132321972907, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He plans to compete at every World Cup the rest of this season, plus January's X Games (which he has won a record five times) and March's World Championships.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 4070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His goals are not results-based, but a broad aim to keep the momentum going from the China podium.\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4156, \"end\": 4161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7021472959811361, \"rank\": 0.2248132321972907, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then next winter, he will bid for a fourth Olympic team.\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is expected that the U.S. will have four men in his event at Milan Cortina.\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4292, \"end\": 4297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.C._Milan\", \"score\": 0.9956021269426091, \"rank\": 0.004417299780861145, \"text\": \"Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.C._Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.C._Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 4298, \"end\": 4305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.496644764219909e-23, \"text\": \"Cortina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The deep field of American halfpipe skiers includes two-time Olympic medalist Alex Ferreira, three-time slopestyle medalist Nick Goepper (who switched to pipe last year), two-time world champion Aaron Blunck and X Games medalists Hunter Hess and Birk Irving.\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4326, \"end\": 4334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998509509372359, \"rank\": 0.0001125981284738463, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 4386, \"end\": 4399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferreira\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Ferreira\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferreira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferreira\"}, {\"begin\": 4432, \"end\": 4444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Goepper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nick Goepper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Goepper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Goepper\"}, {\"begin\": 4503, \"end\": 4508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Brennan\", \"score\": 0.5583963772216901, \"rank\": 0.7743056625271771, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Brennan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Brennan\"}, {\"begin\": 4538, \"end\": 4544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Biden\", \"score\": 0.7154927794387869, \"rank\": 0.3842413275717405, \"text\": \"Hunter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Biden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Biden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise can become the oldest male halfpipe skier in his sport's short Olympic history.\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He can break Shaun White's record as the oldest American Olympian in any of the newest gravity-defying ski and snowboard events (halfpipe, slopestyle, big air).\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4666, \"end\": 4677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaun White\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\"}, {\"begin\": 4701, \"end\": 4709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998509509372359, \"rank\": 0.0001125981284738463, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 4710, \"end\": 4718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 2.892098781998439e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not that many guys that are doing it into their 30s, and it's for a reason,\\\" said Canadian Mike Riddle, who took silver behind Wise in 2014 and has been his coach since 2018.\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4907, \"end\": 4915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999575658393498, \"rank\": 4.215943941940103e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 4916, \"end\": 4927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Riddle\", \"score\": 0.9999780281713398, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Riddle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Riddle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Riddle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is hard to keep pushing yourself.\", \"from\": 5000, \"to\": 5037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The risk versus reward starts to change a little bit as you get older.\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The risk gets a little higher with all the repetitive injuries and things like that.\", \"from\": 5109, \"to\": 5193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So for him to be going for it at 35 has not been done.\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our sport's new, but it's still a feat of athletic achievement, for sure.\\\"\", \"from\": 5249, \"to\": 5323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 5327, \"to\": 5353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5327, \"end\": 5337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.999999984652277, \"rank\": 1.534770837652994e-08, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 5355, \"to\": 5485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 5581, \"to\": 5658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 5660, \"to\": 5680, \"entities\": []}]}"